---
title: Roasted Pumpkin & Double Cheese Pizza with Caramelised Onion & Rocket-Pear Salad
description: This pizza combines bright, roasted veggies and two types of cheese for a flavourful vegetarian 'Za'. It might not be pizza as Italians know it, but it sure does hit the spot.
